[32m│[0m **HTTP-Method Tampering Vulnerability**:                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The `.htaccess` configuration ONLY restricts GET and POST methods. This      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m means **other HTTP methods** like `PUT`, `DELETE`, `PATCH`, `OPTIONS`,       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `CONNECT` may bypass authentication!                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **proofs**                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```bash                                                                      [32m│[0m
